                  <interp inst="t18281023-209-crimeloc1221" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-209-off1218 t18281023-209-crimeloc1221"></join>. On the afternoon of the 22d of October, between three or four o'clock, I was passing down the shop, and saw the prisoner with her right-hand by the side of the counter, and a piece of calico in it; I snatched it out of her hand, threw it on the counter, and gave her a push to go away; I was going in haste to speak to a person in a carriage, but I turned round, and saw the prisoner had something in her apron, and was crossing the road - I went to her, and found a piece of calico in her apron; I took her back.</p>
